Package: rename-to-lowercase
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CLI tool to rename files to lowercase
 A command-line utility that recursively renames all files and
 directories within a specified path to lowercase. It supports
 a force mode (-f) to skip confirmation prompts.
